        <num>CC 3240</num>
        <heading>3240.  Privilege on price of adjudication in case of forced sale</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3240.  Privilege on price of adjudication in case of forced sale.
When the sale was a forced one, the right of the purchaser to the property becomes irrevocable; he owes only the price of adjudication, and over it the creditors exercise their privilege, in the order above prescribed.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
